Bot to post about Deno related updates such as release info, system
downtimes, blog posts and other news from various sources in a Telegram
Channel. Currently posting at https://t.me/deno_news

blog.ts and releases.ts endpoint must be called setup third party cron-jobs
that calls to the endpoint.

status.ts should be hosted somewhere and that deployment URL must be
subscribed in the status page of instatus.com. For example, https://denostatus.com.
